OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772718050
OL,3,CHospitals workers to wear body-worn
OL,4,Ccameras to tackle rising abuse
OL,6,FNHS workers at four major hospitals
OL,7,Fare to be issued with body-worn
OL,8,Fcameras in a major bid to crack down
OL,9,Fon rising levels of violence and abuse
OL,10,Ftowards staff.
OL,12,FThe new technology is being rolled out
OL,13,Facross Bury, Oldham, Rochdale, and
OL,14,FSalford in Greater Manchester.
OL,16,FThe Northern Care Alliance NHS
OL,17,FFoundation Trust, which runs the
OL,18,Fhospitals, says the introduction of
OL,19,Fcameras is "a key part" of their
OL,20,Fcommitment to ensuring the safety of
OL,21,Fworkers, patients, and visitors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
