FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772718050
OL,3,CHospitals workers to wear body-worn
OL,4,Ccameras to tackle rising abuse
OL,6,FIt comes amid growing concerns over
OL,7,Fthe safety of frontline clinical staff
OL,8,Fwho often face "unwanted and abusive"
OL,9,Fbehaviour while trying to provide care.
OL,11,FThe devices will not be filming
OL,12,Fconstantly; instead, they will be worn
OL,13,Fby designated clinical staff and will
OL,14,Fonly be activated if a worker feels
OL,15,Fthreatened.
OL,17,FLeaders say the goal is to build a
OL,18,Fculture where everyone feels "valued
OL,19,Fand respected," regardless of their
OL,20,Fbackground or "lived experiences."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
