OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772718050
OL,3,CHospitals workers to wear body-worn
OL,4,Ccameras to tackle rising abuse
OL,6,FA spokesperson from the trust said:
OL,7,F"Unwanted and abusive behaviours have
OL,8,Fno place in our Trust.
OL,10,F"We expect everyone to be considerate
OL,11,Fand respectful of each other. This is
OL,12,Fabout creating a safer, calmer
OL,13,Fenvironment for everyone who comes
OL,14,Fthrough our doors."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
